{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}],"symbolKind":"struct","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents29OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminateV","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Structure"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Layouts","anchor":"Layouts","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"inverse","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing checkbox indicator and a leading optional image"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Indicator states","anchor":"Indicator-states","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"indeterminate"}]},{"type":"text","text":": mike a prefilled or preticked checkbox, the user did not do anything on it yet"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If you need a checkbox with only two states to manage use instead ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Particular cases","anchor":"Particular-cases","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate"},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In addition, the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate"},{"type":"text","text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"but this component must not be considered as disabled."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component does not follow the right-to-left (RTL) \/ left-to-right (LTR) mode returned by the system as it could have some meaning"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to have for example the indicator in trailing position for LTR mode and vice versa."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, if the component has an icon in leading position (RTL mode) or in trailing position (LTR), the content of the icon is never changed."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It could lead to a loss of meaning or semantics in the icon. Thus a specific flag can be used to flip the icon content whatever the layout direction is."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It prevents the user do implement its own rules to flip or not image."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Accessibility considerations","anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom checkbox trait.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Forbidden by design","anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component."}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component.","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an indeterminate state checkbox","    @Published var selection: OUDSCheckboxIndicatorState = .indeterminate","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Hello world\")","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Hello world\", isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, and an helper text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Bazinga!\", helper: \"Doll-Dagga Buzz-Buzz Ziggety-Zag\")","","    \/\/ A trailing checkbox with a label, an helper text and an icon.","    \/\/ The reversed layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection,","                                  label: \"We live in a fabled world\",","                                  helper: \"Of dreaming boys and wide-eyed girls\",","                                  isReversed: true,","                                  icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"))","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Hello world\")","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label and and icon but with the icon flipped vertically","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(isOn: $selection,","                                  labelText: \"Cocorico !\",","                                  icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                                  flipIcon: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Hello world\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Hello world\", isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you want to manage the RTL mode quite easily and switch your layouts (flip image, indicator in RTL leading i.e. in the right):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    @Environment(\\.layoutDirection) var layoutDirection","","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(isOn: $selection,","                                  labelText: \"Cocorico !\",","                                  icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                                  flipIcon: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft,","                                  isInversed: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Design documentation","anchor":"Design-documentation","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/23f1c1-checkbox","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Since","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.12.0"}]}],"type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some checkboxes components.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use a checkbox with only an indicator prefer instead ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxitemindeterminate"]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate\/init(selection:label:helper:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:isReadOnly:hasDivider:)"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers"},{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate\/body"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate\/View-Implementations"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxitemindeterminate","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some checkboxes components."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use a checkbox with only an indicator prefer instead "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"role":"symbol","title":"OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate"}]},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSCheckboxItem":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItem"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some checkboxes components with labels and icons."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use a checkbox with only an indicator prefer instead "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckbox","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","title":"OUDSCheckboxItem","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxitem","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItem"}]},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The catalog of all components provided by OUDS. It contains also "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"type":"text","text":" extensions and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewModifiers"},{"type":"text","text":" to apply tokens and styles on components and higher-level views."}],"title":"OUDSComponents","type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate":{"identifier":"